      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，仓库节点是要做成判断形状对吧？那如果库存充足走哪条分支？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_Warehouse"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，仓库用菱形判断。库存充足的话，流程要回到车队管理节点，然后继续往下走到库存水位监控。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_Warehouse",
        "Logistics_FleetManagement",
        "Logistics_StockLevel"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把A节点设为车队管理，B节点设为仓库判断，然后加一条Yes分支回到C节点车队管理，再连到D节点库存水位。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A",
        "B",
        "C",
        "D",
        "Logistics_FleetManagement",
        "Logistics_Warehouse",
        "Logistics_StockLevel"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "接下来从库存水位要生成一个跟踪号，这个跟踪号后面还要再复制一份用于后续流程。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_StockLevel",
        "Logistics_TrackingNumber"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "复制一份的意思是E节点生成跟踪号后，F节点再用同样的跟踪号数据？还是两个独立的跟踪号节点？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_TrackingNumber"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是同一个跟踪号流转，E到F是数据传递，F节点之后要回到库存水位做二次确认。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "E",
        "F",
        "Logistics_TrackingNumber",
        "Logistics_StockLevel"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加E节点和F节点都是跟踪号，F连到G节点库存水位。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "E",
        "F",
        "G",
        "Logistics_TrackingNumber",
        "Logistics_StockLevel"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "二次确认后，流程进入配送路线规划，然后再回到仓库节点做最终出库确认。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_DeliveryRoute",
        "Logistics_Warehouse"
