    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "派车之后进入最终的配送路线执行，同时仓库判断的No分支也要直接连到这个配送路线节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_FleetManagement",
        "Logistics_DeliveryRoute",
        "Logistics_Warehouse"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下，K车队管理连到L配送路线，然后B仓库的No分支也连到L配送路线？这样库存不足时跳过中间所有环节？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "K",
        "L",
        "B",
        "Logistics_FleetManagement",
        "Logistics_DeliveryRoute",
        "Logistics_Warehouse"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，库存不足时走快速通道直接到配送路线，但这里有个问题——我刚才说错了，No分支不应该跳到最终配送路线。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_Warehouse",
        "Logistics_DeliveryRoute"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 16,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "抱歉，我重新理一下：No分支应该是跳到另一个处理流程，不是L节点。让我想想……其实按业务逻辑，库存不足时应该直接触发补货，但当前流程里我们先简化成直接连到L配送路线做异常处理。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "B",
        "L",
        "Logistics_Warehouse",
        "Logistics_DeliveryRoute"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 17,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "那就是保持B的No分支连到L？但L已经在K后面了，这样画出来B→L和K→L都会指向L，形成汇聚。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "B",
        "K",
        "L",
        "Logistics_Warehouse",
        "Logistics_FleetManagement",
        "Logistics_DeliveryRoute"
